bayou.tcp

Class TcpAddress

  • java.lang.Object
    • bayou.tcp.TcpAddress

  • public class TcpAddress
extends Object
    Address of a TCP service.

    The address includes host and port. Additionally, ssl=true if SSL is required by the service.
